  <entry>
    <title>Coding_C[03]</title>
    <link href="/2026/05/27/Coding-C-3/"/>
    <url>/2026/05/27/Coding-C-3/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="3-分割字符串"><a href="#3-分割字符串" class="headerlink" title="#3 分割字符串"></a>#3 分割字符串</h3><p>题目要求将字符串进行切割，输出一个字符矩阵。</p><span id="more"></span><p>即两组之间用回车分行。<br>对于不足8个字符的行，用0补全至8个字符。</p><h4 id="1-示例"><a href="#1-示例" class="headerlink" title="1.示例"></a>1.示例</h4><p>输入字符串：HelloAkira<br>输出：<br>    HelloAki<br>    ra000000</p><h4 id="2-思路"><a href="#2-思路" class="headerlink" title="2.思路"></a>2.思路</h4><ul><li>首先判断输入的字符串中字符个数是否是8的倍数。</li><li>如果字符总数不是8的倍数，那么利用for循环将原本的字符串补到8的倍数。</li><li>补上字符串的’\0’</li><li>按每8个字符一组的方式分割已经处理完的字符串。</li></ul><h4 id="3-程序"><a href="#3-程序" class="headerlink" title="3.程序"></a>3.程序</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> str[<span class="hljs-number">150</span>];<br>    fgets(str, <span class="hljs-number">150</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">stdin</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> length_original = <span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(str);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (length_original &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span> &amp;&amp; str[length_original - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>)<br>    &#123;<br>        str[length_original - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;<br>        length_original--;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/* 以上为输入的字符串的预处理，即将fgets()函数引入的&#x27;\n&#x27;去除 */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> need = length_original % <span class="hljs-number">8</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//计算字符串是否是8的倍数，如果不是，则求最后一行的字符数。</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (need != <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">//字符串不是8的倍数，需要处理</span><br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> loop_1 = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; loop_1 &lt; <span class="hljs-number">8</span> - need; loop_1++)<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//loop_1 &lt; 8 - need是用来作为补齐最后一行的依据，即最后一行还需要补几个零</span><br>        &#123;<br>            str[loop_1 + length_original] = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//补零</span><br>        &#125;<br>        str[length_original + <span class="hljs-number">8</span> - need] = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//还原字符串末尾</span><br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> count = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(str); i++)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c&quot;</span>, str[i]);<br>        count++;<span class="hljs-comment">//每输出一个字符，计数加一</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (count % <span class="hljs-number">8</span> == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">//计数达到8的倍数，输出回车</span><br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
