  <entry>
    <title>Coding_C[02]</title>
    <link href="/2026/05/27/Coding-C-2/"/>
    <url>/2026/05/27/Coding-C-2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="2-统计某个指定字符的出现次数"><a href="#2-统计某个指定字符的出现次数" class="headerlink" title="#2 统计某个指定字符的出现次数"></a>#2 统计某个指定字符的出现次数</h3><p>对于数字，统计出现次数；对于字母，统计其大小写出现的次数的和。</p><span id="more"></span><h4 id="1-示例"><a href="#1-示例" class="headerlink" title="1.示例"></a>1.示例</h4><p>测试字符串： HelloWorld<br>指定字符： o<br>输出： 2</p><h4 id="2-思路"><a href="#2-思路" class="headerlink" title="2.思路"></a>2.思路</h4><p>利用ASC II码对应的值来进行判断。<br>①数字0~9，则直接利用其对应的ASC II码进行计数。<br>②对于字母，可以先将所有的大写字母全部转换成小写字母，然后再进行判断。</p><h4 id="3-程序"><a href="#3-程序" class="headerlink" title="3.程序"></a>3.程序</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">char</span> str[<span class="hljs-number">1000</span>];<br>fgets(str, <span class="hljs-number">1000</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">stdin</span>);<span class="hljs-comment">//测试样例时出现过数组越界，因此将数组长度调整至1500</span><br><span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> count = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>scanf_s(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c&quot;</span>, &amp;ch);<span class="hljs-comment">//读取用于判断的目标字符</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch &gt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; ch &lt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span>) ch = ch + <span class="hljs-number">32</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//如果给定的字符是大写字母，则转换为小写字母</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt;= <span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(str); i++)<br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (str[i] &gt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; str[i] &lt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Z&#x27;</span>) str[i] += <span class="hljs-number">32</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//当前读取到的字符是大写字母吗？如果是，则转换为小写字母。</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (str[i] == ch) count++;<span class="hljs-comment">//比对当前取出的字符与指定的字符，如果相同，计数加一</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, count);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
